TNode {.final, acyclic.} = object
  when defined(useNodeIds):
    id*: int
  info*: TLineInfo
  flags*: TNodeFlags
  case kind*: TNodeKind
  of nkCharLit .. nkUInt64Lit:
    intVal*: BiggestInt
  of nkFloatLit .. nkFloat128Lit:
    floatVal*: BiggestFloat
  of nkStrLit .. nkTripleStrLit:
